{"tid":1554870,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[共識題]十月一你想做咩？","createTime":"2019-09-09T06:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T03:52:21.000Z","uid":8948,"like":13,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"5e2cec62dafa288d37115391db71c9de29a74a8a","tid":1554870,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"我認為呢幾個禮拜連續多次活動已經令我地既共識散左好多<br />\n好多勇武都冇辦法可以協調到邊一日係可以集結<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唯一大家有共識既就係十月一日一定要搞大佢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好啦，問題黎啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁點樣搞大佢先？</span></span><br />\n睇返成場運動，最有代表性既幾場戰役<br />\n<br />\n和理非：818和理非吹大雞癱瘓港島<br />\n勇武：71攻入立法會／85各區圍攻狗屋<br />\n<br />\n而去到第三個月，相信大家都知道已經唔可以再分當日既活動係「和理非」抑或係「勇武」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為無論咩活動，黑警都係會出手打壓，佢地已經唔會再care你係咪和理非，亦唔會care形象，佢地只係想「打死晒班曱甴」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n個人認為活動既性質可以分為<br />\n遍地開花式 ／ 集中式<br />\n<br />\n首先我地就大方向投票<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持集中癱瘓全港島，落中共面，決一死戰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擺明駐重兵港島，應該避其鋒芒，遍地開花<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亦希望大家投完票可以理性討論，be humble，勿互屌分化</span></span>"},{"pid":"938b10a14c0cb926fff584d5ab3319dab025eaf8","tid":1554870,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"支持獨立思考"},{"pid":"984fe4b73d6a9a720152e17c7cf166833f8fa1eb","tid":1554870,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:51:08.000Z","msg":"【913 八月十五】 金鐘悼義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554687</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XySvw4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXySvw4Z.jpg&h=8251e762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqGL5pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqGL5pZ.jpg&h=af6e3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dafe4f0f2f3a4838bab097fcb5e1f0f0a25965d","tid":1554870,"uid":132999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:51:17.000Z","msg":"想睇煙花<br />\n<br />\nSorry 係煙火"},{"pid":"78402f211b731303e3e72dec9e0b0a94efadec01","tid":1554870,"uid":22506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:52:07.000Z","msg":"覺得玩哂十八區遍地開花串過淨係搞港島"},{"pid":"bd357ce9a48bf6b45e3a3aee870aa5ecc429ace5","tid":1554870,"uid":30384,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:52:54.000Z","msg":"想睇人人手持一枝美國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4112e166703917ab7ac15aff7bd1804be8413905","tid":1554870,"uid":280285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:53:52.000Z","msg":"全民舉美國旗行街。<br />\n大小不拘，著美國旗服飾也可。<br />\n加上不同宗教集會，國慶普天同慶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1fd34d930ceb64de176179acd81688104eb591","tid":1554870,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78402f211b731303e3e72dec9e0b0a94efadec01","tid":1554870,"uid":22506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:52:07.000Z","msg":"覺得玩哂十八區遍地開花串過淨係搞港島"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:54:07.000Z","msg":"其實係，而且你攻一座堡壘，有效既兵力只有100人<br />\n但當你攻十座堡壘，有效既兵力就會有1000人"},{"pid":"53b5d189e20684ad8574b85cf75ba60cf5bbbe7d","tid":1554870,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"其實政權既實體就係黑警<br />\n希望大家明白，呢個香港已經再冇警察<br />\n有既只係維護殺人政權既維穩部隊"},{"pid":"b30a688397ed797a7e3719dbdcc3e604f0891076","tid":1554870,"uid":253183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bd357ce9a48bf6b45e3a3aee870aa5ecc429ace5","tid":1554